
 mkinitramfs
 ------------

 This is an initramfs creator for Pardus, Mkinitramfs part is written in Python, 
the init script running in boot process is written as shell script (ash compatib
le).

 Init script creates a temporary initramfs to do initial system booting tasks (st
orage probing, graphic card initialization) for installed systems and live syste
ms. It can also be used as a very basic rescue system for failsafe operations.


 For initramfs options, see the output of

 mkinitramfs --help



